  "title": "Sales Engineer (MNC)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>MNC Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $4500 - $5000 + Transport allowance + Incentive + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Central</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working days: Monday to Friday</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 9am to 6pm</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Execute sales plans to grow the customer and distributor based in the assigned region</li>\n  <li>Visit consultants, contractors, and project sites to promote products and generate leads</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular product trainings and technical seminars</li>\n  <li>Provide pre- and post-sales technical support to clients and partners</li>\n  <li>Monitor market trends, customer feedback, and competitor activities</li>\n  <li>Prepare and submit sales reports, forecasts, and activity updates as required</li>\n  <li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess minimum Diploma or Bachelor’s Degree in Electrical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Possess minimum 2 years of sales experience in electrical installation products</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
